Summary - Supporting a Sales VP, 7 Directors and 40 Sales Managers on people matters. 
- Coaching managers to take ownership of all people management and HR practices and facilitating the implementation of people management processes;  
- Collaborating with leaders and other colleagues within businesses and HR organization to ensure best possible use of HR knowledge and practices to meet the business needs;  
- Supporting managers in organizational change management and development & succession planning and talent management; 
- Driving implementation of Strategic Competence development plans and promoting different modes of learning and different learning solutions; 
- Supporting business specific desired diversity and recruitment plans creation and implementation; 
- Ensuring the delivery of a full scope of HR services and acting as an expert of global HR processes, policies, practices and tools and ensuring that their application is in line with the local legislation ;  
- Ensuring the quality of HR data and HR products, tools and process implementation; 
- Co-operating with third parties (e.g. Local authorities, workers councils, workers representatives) and working with external vendors to administer HR services; 
- Ensuring and supporting the implementation of the performance management processes according to the global policies and guidelines; 
- Driving and participating to the co. / Region wide projects e.g. integration activities;  
- Driving and promoting company’s culture and values; 
- Change Management processes (M&A) 

